{"word":"G2234 - ἡδέως - hēdéōs - hay-deh'-oce - Gladly","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἡδέως</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hēdéōs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hay-deh'-oce</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Gladly</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"விருப்பத்தோடே, சந்தோஷமாய் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"with pleasure, gladly"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Adverb from a derivative of the base of <a href=\"#/G2237 - ἡδονή - hēdonḗ - hay-don-ay'/2237\">G2237</a>; <i>sweetly</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>with pleasure:</i> - gladly.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}